主要翻译
 
expedition n (organized journey)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese （有组织的）远行 yǒu zǔ zhī de yuǎn xíng  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 探险 yǒu zǔ zhī de yuǎn xíng，tàn xiǎn 
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 远征 yǒu zǔ zhī de yuǎn xíng，yuǎn zhēng 
 -- The explorers planned an expedition in order to map the river.
 
expedition n (people on journey)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 远征队（员） yuǎn zhēng duì yuán  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 探险队（员） yuǎn zhēng duì yuán，tàn xiǎn duì yuán 
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 考察队（员） yuǎn zhēng duì yuán，kǎo chá duì yuán 
 -- Four members of the expedition died from illness.

其他翻译
 
expedition n formal, uncountable (promptness)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 迅速 xùn sù TC Traditional Chinese 迅速  
 -- The expedition with which the paperwork was processed surprised everyone.

复合形式： 
 
fishing expedition n figurative (legal proceeding)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 远距离求证  (法庭审讯)
 -- 备注 : 指在庭审中询问松散的问题以获得信息
 
fishing expedition, fishing trip n figurative (attempt to gain information)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 非法调查  
 
go on a fishing expedition v expr figurative (hunt for unspecified evidence)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 盘问 pán wèn  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 摸底 pán wèn，mō dǐ 
 -- In the US, police are not allowed to go on a fishing expedition in your house without a search warrant.
 
hunting expedition n (group outing to hunt animals)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 打猎探险 dǎ liè tàn xiǎn TC Traditional Chinese 打獵探險  
 -- The hunting expedition set off early to look for wild boar.
 
scouting expedition n (boy scouts' outing)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 童子军探险活动 tóng zǐ jūn tàn xiǎn huó dòng  

在这些条目还发现' expedition '：
在英文解释里：
expeditionary - hunting trip

